Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二  你还困吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子  拿手机给我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.72,0:00:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是警察吗  有人非法入侵
