Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.25,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance,one more chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:45.60,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one more chance,one more chance
